author: Tucker Doherty
title: What the president said he did on the virus — and what he actually did
description: A list of his key moves released by Trump's campaign overstates some of his actions – and leaves out the inactions.
content:
Heres all the ways the president said he took action coupled with a reality check for what really happened.
